public class ComponentsInPageManagement
extends com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.widget.LayoutContainer
implements IDetailPanel, IPaletteComponentsReceiver

Manages the Components and their logical dependencies tree within a Page.
Panel with the list of portal's components and their dependencies tree.
Forwards the Change event fired by the tree Components in Page.

Author:
Manuel Ruiz
